Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 9
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Are the magical dreams of Madoka Kaname suddenly becoming a reality?
Title: PUELLA MAGI MADOKA MAGICA, VOL. 1
Author: Magica Quartet

Description: Oz, who is condemned to an abyss for a mysterious sin, sets out to investigate with an Alice, an equally mysterious girl he met in exile.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 10

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 5
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: In this romance (?) story, Tetsuhiro Morinaga, a university student, is in love with his mentor, who is straight and homophobic.
Title: THE TYRANT FALLS IN LOVE, VOL. 6
Author: Hinako Takanaga

Description: The SOS Brigade is a school club dedicated to meeting time travelers or aliens or anyone fantastic. Their main mission: keep Haruhi happy because she has the power to destroy the universe (but doesnâ€™t know it).
Title: THE MELANCHOLY OF HARUHI SUZUMIYA, VOL. 12
Author: Nagaru Tanigawa

Description: The backstory is complicated, but the gist is this: four 15-year-old male friends must turn an outcast wallflower into a lovely lady.
Title: THE WALLFLOWER, VOL. 28
Author: Tomoko Hayakawa

Description: This series is about college students who are drawn together by their shared love of modern visual culture.
Title: GENSHIKEN, OMNIBUS 1

Description: Himari is a cat-spirit sworn to protect teenage Yuuto.
Title: OMAMORI HIMARI, VOL. 7
Author: Milan Matra

Description: Naruto and his allies face off against a horde of ninja soldiers, some of whom are back from the dead and former friends.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 56
